refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.returnvalues;


 A permutation of the values of array.



 Array keys of the input array will not be preserved;
 the returned &array; will be a list (array_is_list).

  &reftitle.examples;

   Random\Randomizer::shuffleArray example


<?php
$r = new \Random\Randomizer();

$fruits = [ 'red' => '🍎', 'green' => '🥝', 'yellow' => '🍌', 'pink' => '🍑', 'purple' => '🍇' ];

// Shuffle array:
echo "Salad: ", implode(', ', $r->shuffleArray($fruits)), "\n";

// Shuffle again:
echo "Another Salad: ", implode(', ', $r->shuffleArray($fruits)), "\n";
?>


   &example.outputs.similar;


Salad: 🍎, 🥝, 🍇, 🍌, 🍑
Another Salad: 🍑, 🍇, 🥝, 🍎, 🍌
